Mary Ann Jackson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Ann_Jackson 0 Mary Ann Jackson (January 14, 1923 – December 17, 2003) was an American child actress who appeared in the Our Gang short subjects series from 1928 to 1931. She was a native of Los Angeles, California.
